# Accessibility rules

Implement the component using the ARIA combobox/listbox pattern.

Required:
- Input `role="combobox"`
- `aria-expanded`
- `aria-controls`
- `aria-activedescendant` when an option is highlighted
- List `role="listbox"`
- Option `role="option"`
- `aria-selected` on options

Keyboard behavior:
- ArrowDown opens list and moves highlight down.
- ArrowUp opens list and moves highlight up.
- Enter selects highlighted option.
- Escape closes dropdown.
- Tab allows normal focus movement and closes dropdown.
- Mouse selection must not break focus behavior.
